    "img": "systems/pf1/icons/feats/combat-expertise.jpg",
    "name": "Combat Expertise",
    "system": {
      "description": {
        "value": "<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf1.feats.Item.NFxHebU1XhEs5WJh]{Combat Expertise}</p><p>You can choose to take a \u20131 penalty on melee attack rolls and combat maneuver checks to gain a +1 dodge bonus to your Armor Class. When your base attack bonus reaches +4, and every +4 thereafter, the penalty increases by \u20131 and the dodge bonus increases by +1.</p><p>You can only choose to use this feat when you declare that you are making an attack or a full-attack action with a melee weapon. The effects of this feat last until your next turn.</p>",
        "instructions": ""
      },
      "tags": [],
      "changes": [
        {
          "_id": "6cxoFKCg",
          "formula": "-(1 + (floor(@attributes.bab.total / 4)))",
          "target": "mattack",
          "type": "untyped"
        },
